            <history-note id="DLM1673802"><amended-provision>Section 44(3)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 October 2008</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM1102383">section 130(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Policing
