              <history-note id="DLM2490415"><amended-provision>Schedule 5 clause
2(h)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>17 October 2009</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM2141072">section 161(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Anti-Money
